					"value": "Dialog which happens when the player gets too close to the marching army. In the dialog the player can either back off or continue, and if you continue you get arrested and either thrown in prison in Moonrise Towers or in Corpse Pit in the Mind Flayer colony if the Prison Break has already happened."
				}
			}
		}
	}
}